{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h2 id=\"1-react-life-cycle-methods-overview\"><a href=\"#1-react-life-cycle-methods-overview\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1 React Life Cycle Methods Overview</h2>\n<h4 id=\"birth--mounting\"><a href=\"#birth--mounting\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Birth / Mounting</h4>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Initialize / Construction</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>getDefaultProps() (React.createClass) or MyComponent.defaultProps (ES6 class)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>getInitialState() (React.createClass) or this.state = ... (ES6 constructor)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>componentWillMount()</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>render()</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Children initialization &#x26; life cycle kickoff</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>componentDidMount()</p>\n<h4 id=\"growth--update\"><a href=\"#growth--update\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Growth / Update</h4>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>componentWillReceiveProps()</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>shouldComponentUpdate()</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>componentWillUpdate()</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>render()</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Children Life cycle methods</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>componentDidUpdate()</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h4 id=\"death--unmount\"><a href=\"#death--unmount\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Death / Unmount</h4>\n<ol>\n<li>componentWillUnmount()</li>\n<li>Children Life cycle methods</li>\n<li>Instance destroyed for Garbage Collection</li>\n</ol>\n<p>setState\n\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/react-lifecycle-flow-chart-states-4c6ddf531a4b655c780d019aa0b31834-fa619.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 690px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 40.27370478983382%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"setState\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/react-lifecycle-flow-chart-states-4c6ddf531a4b655c780d019aa0b31834-44d6a.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/react-lifecycle-flow-chart-states-4c6ddf531a4b655c780d019aa0b31834-f4799.png 173w,\n/static/react-lifecycle-flow-chart-states-4c6ddf531a4b655c780d019aa0b31834-b3b1d.png 345w,\n/static/react-lifecycle-flow-chart-states-4c6ddf531a4b655c780d019aa0b31834-44d6a.png 690w,\n/static/react-lifecycle-flow-chart-states-4c6ddf531a4b655c780d019aa0b31834-fa619.png 1023w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 690px) 100vw, 690px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<h2 id=\"2-growthupdate-in-depth\"><a href=\"#2-growthupdate-in-depth\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2 Growth/Update In-depth</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>The Growth phase is triggered in three different ways: changeing of props, changing of state or calling forceUpdate();</li>\n<li>Props are immutable by the Component itself.</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"3-why-react-need-key-\"><a href=\"#3-why-react-need-key-\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3 why react need key ?</h2>\n<p>By having an identifier based on the data content instead of order, we can help optimize the Component rendering.</p>\n<h2 id=\"4-小结\"><a href=\"#4-%E5%B0%8F%E7%BB%93\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>4 小结</h2>\n<p>本书主要介绍了react声明周期内相关知识点，但是介绍的是比较深层次的，比较细化的一些东西。<br>\n英文的原因，有写地方没有太明白，有时间再看一次。</p>","timeToRead":1,"excerpt":"1 React Life Cycle Methods Overview Birth / Mounting Initialize / Construction getDefaultProps() (React.createClass) or MyComponent…","frontmatter":{"title":"react-indepth 读书笔记","cover":null,"date":"2017-01-20T22:00:00.000Z","category":"books","tags":["books"]},"fields":{"nextTitle":"font weight 数值名称对应表","nextSlug":"/css/font-weight/","prevTitle":"三体读书笔记","prevSlug":"/books/the-three-body-problem/","slug":"/books/react in-depth/","date":"2017-01-19T16:00:00.000Z"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/books/react in-depth/"}}